IRC Moderator Usage of Bot Commands

BANS should be handled by BotOfLegends (Angela).
Chanserv (Rizon) doesn't handle temporary bans well. Angela has a memory system.

Muting channel:

say: "!mute"
or
say: "!unmute"

BAN SYSTEM:

type !ban <nickname> <duration> <reason>

examples:

!ban Angela 1 Abuse
  -- Will ban Angela for 1 minute
!ban Angela 3h Abuse
  -- Will ban Angela for 3 hours
!ban Angela 72h Abuse
  -- Will ban Angela for 3 days
!ban Angela 2w Abuse
  -- Will ban Angela for 2 weeks
!ban Angela 0 Abuse
  -- Will ban Angela for ever.
